1. Tm tt (abstract)

D n ny trnh by mt gii php t ng ha trong vic to ni dung qung co lin quan n s kin Black Friday v ng ti trn mng x hi Twitter. Quy trnh da trn mt h thng pipeline c thit k vi cc cng c tin tin nh Apache NiFi, Apache Kafka, v Apache Spark. D liu c thu thp t Twitter API thng qua Apache NiFi, sau c truyn ti v x l theo thi gian thc bng Apache Kafka. Spark c s dng thc hin cc bc tin x l, chuyn i d liu v chun b cho vic hun luyn m hnh Text Generation. M hnh ny, da trn cc kin trc hc su nh LSTM hoc GPT, c hun luyn to ra cc bi ng c ni dung sng to v ph hp vi ch Black Friday. H thng cng tch hp API Twitter t ng ha vic ng bi, gip tng hiu qu tip cn khch hng. Kt qu thc nghim cho thy h thng c kh nng to ni dung vi cht lng cao v tit kim ng k thi gian cng nh cng sc. Ngoi ra, cn cung cp tnh linh hot trong vic ty chnh cc chin lc tip th v c tim nng m rng sang nhiu ng dng khc trong lnh vc x l ngn ng t nhin. y l mt bc tin quan trng trong vic ng dng cng ngh AI gii quyt cc bi ton thc t, c bit trong lnh vc tip th s.

2. Gii thiu (introduction)

Trong thi i k thut s ngy nay, d liu khng ch ng vai tr nh mt ngun ti nguyn quan trng m cn c xem l yu t quyt nh hiu r hn v x hi v th trng. Mng x hi, c bit l Twitter, tr thnh mt trong nhng nn tng giao tip v truyn ti thng tin ph bin nht trn ton cu. Vi hng triu bi ng mi ngy, vic duy tr ni dung hp dn v ph hp vi xu hng l mt thch thc khng nh i vi cc c nhn, doanh nghip v t chc. Vic sng to ni dung th cng i hi nhiu thi gian, cng sc v s sng to, iu ny i khi lm gim hiu sut hoc khng p ng kp thi nhng thay i lin tc ca thng tin. khc phc, s pht trin ca tr tu nhn to, c bit l cc m hnh Text Generation, mang li mt gii php t ph trong vic t ng ha sng to ni dung. Cc m hnh ny s dng hc su (Deep Learning) phn tch d liu vn bn v to ra nhng ni dung mi mt cch t nhin, ph hp vi ng cnh. y l cch tip cn hiu qu to ra cc bi vit c cht lng cao v ng thi gim thiu chi ph v thi gian.

D n ny tp trung vo ng dng Text Generation nhm to ra ni dung bi vit trn Twitter da trn cc m hnh hc su hin i. Thay v ch dng li vic x l d liu, h thng ny gip t ng ha ton b qu trnh sng to ni dung t khu phn tch n khu xut bn, vi mc tiu m bo ni dung c to ra khng ch sng to m cn mang tnh c nhn ha v bt kp xu hng. H thng Text Generation c th c trin khai trong nhiu lnh vc thc t nh tip th s (digital marketing), qun l truyn thng x hi, phn tch cm xc (sentiment analysis), hoc d bo xu hng. Chng hn, cc doanh nghip c th s dng cng ngh ny xy dng chin lc truyn thng hiu qu hn, to cc bi vit tng tc vi khch hng, hoc pht hin sm nhng thay i trong hnh vi ngi dng. Vi s pht trin khng ngng ca tr tu nhn to v hc su, d n khng ch dng li vic to ra nhng ni dung sng to m cn t nn mng cho nhng h thng thng minh hn, c kh nng p ng nhanh chng v linh hot trong th gii s ha ang thay i tng ngy. ng dng Text Generation trn Twitter chnh l minh chng cho tim nng v hn ca cng ngh trong vic thay i cch chng ta sng to v giao tip trong k nguyn 4.0.

3. S kin trc d n

4. D liu (Data)

4.1. D liu thu thp t Twitter

Trong ch ny, chng ta s dng Twitter API truy cp v tng tc vi d liu t Twitter. D liu ny bao gm cc tweet, thng tin v ngi dng, xu hng (trends), v nhiu thng tin khc lin quan n hot ng trn Twitter.

D liu nhn c t Twitter l mt JSON object cha thng tin chi tit v mt tweet, bao gm cc siu d liu lin quan n tweet, video, v thng tin v ngi dng.

Cu trc d liu

Thng tin chung v Tweet

  • tweet_id: ID duy nht ca tweet.
  • creation_date: Ngy v gi to tweet.
  • text: Ni dung ca tweet.
  • language: Ngn ng ca tweet.
  • favorite_count: S lt thch tweet nhn.
  • retweet_count: S lt retweet.
  • reply_count: S lt tr li.
  • quote_count: S lt tweet c trch dn.
  • views: S lt xem ca tweet.
  • expanded_url: URL y ca tweet.
  • source: Nn tng t tweet c ng ti.

Thng tin v Video v Media

  • media_url: Danh sch URL ca hnh nh i din ca video.
  • video_url: Danh sch cc URL ca cc phin bn video vi cc mc bitrate khc nhau:
    • URL m3u8 dnh cho streaming.
    • URL MP4 vi cc bitrate khc nhau nh 632000, 950000, v 2176000.
  • extended_entities: Thng tin chi tit v media trong tweet:
    • media: Danh sch cc media nh km trong tweet.
    • type: Loi media (video).
    • sizes: Cc kch thc c sn ca media (large, medium, small, thumb).
    • video_info: Thng tin chi tit v video:
      • T l (aspect_ratio).
      • Thi lng (duration_millis).
      • Cc phin bn video (variants) vi bitrate khc nhau.

Thng tin v Ngi dng

  • user_id: ID ca ngi dng.
  • username: Tn ng nhp ca ngi dng.
  • name: Tn hin th ca ngi dng.
  • follower_count: S ngi theo di.
  • following_count: S ngi dng ang theo di.
  • favourites_count: S lng tweet nh du yu thch.
  • is_private: Kim tra ti khon c ch ring t (null c ngha l khng c thng tin).
  • is_verified: Ngi dng c tick xanh xc thc khng.
  • is_blue_verified: Ngi dng c xc thc Blue Verified khng.
  • location: V tr ca ngi dng.
  • profile_pic_url: URL nh i din ca ngi dng.
  • profile_banner_url: URL banner ca ngi dng.
  • description: Phn m t ca ngi dng.
  • external_url: URL bn ngoi lin kt vi h s ca ngi dng.
  • number_of_tweets: S lng tweet ngi dng ng.
  • bot: Xc nh ngi dng c phi bot khng.
  • timestamp: Thi im to ti khon (di dng UNIX timestamp).

Cc trng khc

  • retweet: Kim tra tweet c phi l retweet khng.
  • in_reply_to_status_id: ID ca tweet m tweet ny tr li.
  • quoted_status_id: ID ca tweet c trch dn.
  • binding_values: Cc gi tr lin kt.
  • conversation_id: ID cuc hi thoi cha tweet ny.
  • retweet_status: Trng thi retweet.
  • quoted_status: Trng thi trch dn.
  • bookmark_count: S lt nh du ca tweet.
  • community_note: Ghi ch cng ng.

4.2. D liu training model

Sau khi thu thp c file JSON cha d liu Tweets, vic tin x l l mt bc quan trng chun b d liu cho cc bc tip theo. Trong trng hp ny, mc tiu l ch gi li ni dung ca cc Tweets (thuc tnh text) v chuyn i d liu sang nh dng file .txt d dng s dng trong vic training m hnh.

Cc bc tin x l

  1. c file JSON
    c d liu t file JSON cha thng tin tweet.

  2. Trch xut ni dung Tweets
    Ch gi li trng text trong mi i tng Tweet.

  3. Lm sch d liu vn bn

    • Loi b cc k t c bit, lin kt (URLs), v hashtags.
    • Chun ha vn bn (v d: chuyn ton b ch vit thng).

  4. Lu tr d liu vo file .txt

    • Ghi ton b ni dung vn bn (mi dng l mt Tweet) vo mt file .txt.
    • File .txt ny s c s dng trong vic training m hnh NLP.

Kt qu

Sau khi hon thnh bc tin x l, chng ta c mt tp .txt cha ni dung ca cc tweet qua x l. Tp ny sn sng c s dng trong cc bc hun luyn tip theo ca pipeline.

5. Phng php (Methods)

5.1 tng thut ton

gii quyt bi ton sinh vn bn da trn chui k t, nhm s dng thut ton LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory), mt bin th ni bt ca mng hi quy tun hon (RNN - Recurrent Neural Network). LSTM c thit k khc phc hn ch ca RNN truyn thng, c bit l hin tng vanishing gradient khi x l cc chui d liu di.

Thng qua c ch lu gi v loi b thng tin linh hot, LSTM c kh nng ghi nh cc mi quan h di hn gia cc phn t trong chui, gip m hnh nhn din ng cnh v mi lin kt gia cc k t. y l l do LSTM c chn cho bi ton x l ngn ng t nhin (NLP) ni s gn kt ng ngha gia cc k t v t vng ng vai tr quan trng trong vic to ra vn bn c ngha.

5.2 C ch hot ng ca LSTM

Mi LSTM unit c thit k vi ba cng chnh gip kim sot lung thng tin:

5.2.1. Cng qun (Forget Gate):

  • Quyt nh thng tin no t trng thi trc cn c loi b. Cng thc hot ng:
    math
f_t = \sigma(W_f \cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_f)
    • $f_t$: Vector ch s qun, gi tr nm trong khong ([0, 1]).
    • $W_f, b_f$: Trng s v bias.
    • $h_{t-1}$: Trng thi n t bc trc.
    • $x_t$: u vo hin ti.
    • $\sigma$: Hm kch hot sigmoid, xc nh mc gi li thng tin.

5.2.2. Cng vo (Input Gate):

  • Quyt nh thng tin mi no cn c lu gi vo trng thi hin ti. Hai cng thc chnh:
    math
i_t = \sigma(W_i \cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_i)

    math
\tilde{C}_t = \tanh(W_C \cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_C)
    • $i_t$: Vector quyt nh mc lu gi thng tin.
    • $\tilde{C}_t$: Trng thi nh c xut, biu din thng tin mi.
    • $\tanh$: Hm kch hot hyperbolic tangent.

5.2.3. Cng u ra (Output Gate):

  • Quyt nh thng tin no t trng thi hin ti c xut ra lm u ra. Cng thc:
    math
o_t = \sigma(W_o \cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_o)

    math
h_t = o_t \cdot \tanh(C_t)
    • $o_t$: Vector kim sot u ra.
    • $h_t$: Trng thi n ti thi im hin ti.

Ba cng ny phi hp kim sot thng tin trong mi bc thi gian, gip LSTM gi li thng tin quan trng t cc bc trc v hc mi lin h gia cc phn t trong chui d liu.

S minh ha LSTM

Di y l s minh ha mt cell LSTM, bao gm cc cng chnh v trng thi:

  • Cng qun (Forget Gate): Loi b thng tin khng cn thit.
  • Cng vo (Input Gate): Cp nht thng tin mi vo trng thi nh.
  • Cng u ra (Output Gate): Quyt nh thng tin no s c s dng lm u ra.

5.3 Hm mc tiu v thut ton ti u

5.3.1 Hm mc tiu (Categorical Cross-Entropy):

Dng o lng s khc bit gia phn phi xc sut thc t v d on. Cng thc:

math
\text{Loss} = -\sum_{i=1}^{n} y_i \log(\hat{y}_i)

Trong :

  • $y_i$: Vector nhn thc t (one-hot encoding).
  • $\hat{y}_i$: Xc sut d on cho tng lp.

5.3.2 Thut ton ti u ha (Adam Optimizer):

Adam kt hp gia Momentum v RMSProp, gip tng tc hi t v ti u ha trng s hiu qu. iu ny lm gim yu cu tinh chnh siu tham s trong qu trnh hun luyn.

5.4 Li ch ca vic s dng LSTM

  1. Ghi nh ng cnh di hn:

    • LSTM c kh nng lu gi thng tin quan trng trong cc chui di, gip tng chnh xc khi d on chui vn bn.

  2. X l thng tin linh hot:

    • Cc c ch cng gip m hnh lc v lu tr thng tin cn thit, gim thiu tnh trng qu ti d liu.

  3. Hi t nhanh chng:

    • Adam Optimizer gip m hnh t hiu sut cao m khng cn iu chnh siu tham s phc tp.

6. Thc nghim, kt qu, v tho lun (Experiments, Results, and Discussions)

6.1 Cu hnh thc nghim

Quy trnh tng qut

H thng c thit k da trn pipeline tch hp cc cng c hin i nh Apache Kafka, Apache Spark, v m hnh LSTM. Pipeline ny khng ch gip x l d liu theo thi gian thc m cn m bo tnh chnh xc v hiu qu trong vic sinh vn bn ph hp vi chin dch qung co Black Friday.

  • Giai on u tin bt u bng vic s dng Apache Kafka thu thp d liu t Twitter API. Kafka c s dng nh mt trung tm lu tr v x l d liu streaming, cho php d liu lun chuyn lin tc t nhiu ngun khc nhau. D liu c truyn t Kafka sang Apache Spark, ni x l chnh din ra.
  • Trong giai on th hai, Apache Spark m nhim nhim v x l d liu thi gian thc bng cch thc hin cc bc nh chun ha, trch xut schema, v chuyn i d liu th thnh dng c cu trc. Spark Streaming m bo d liu u vo c x l mt cch lin tc v khng b gin on, nh vo tnh nng checkpoint v fault tolerance (kh nng phc hi li).
  • Giai on cui cng l s dng d liu c chun b hun luyn m hnh LSTM. Vi kh nng hc tp t cc chui k t v mi lin kt gia chng, m hnh LSTM sinh ra cc bi vit sng to, ph hp vi chin lc tip th Black Friday
  • Nh thit k ny, h thng t c s tch hp lin mch gia cc cng c, gim thiu sai st v m bo tnh ng b trong ton b quy trnh.

6.1.1 Cc cng c v cu hnh

Apache Kafka

Apache Kafka ng vai tr nh mt trung tm x l d liu streaming. N cho php d liu c thu thp v truyn i mt cch nhanh chng. Cc cu hnh c th nh kafka.bootstrap.servers m bo Kafka kt ni vi Spark v cc ngun d liu, trong d liu c ly t topic "blackfriday". y l yu t quan trng trong vic duy tr d liu lin tc.

Apache Spark

Apache Spark ng vai tr l cng c x l chnh trong pipeline. Spark khng ch x l d liu m cn chun b cc tp vn bn v trch xut schema, m bo rng d liu u vo lun trng thi tt nht trc khi a vo m hnh LSTM. Mt s bc quan trng bao gm:

  • Chun ha d liu: m bo tnh ng nht ca d liu, loi b cc k t khng cn thit.
  • Trch xut schema: Lu schema di dng JSON ti s dng v duy tr s nht qun trong cc bc x l k tip.

M hnh LSTM

LSTM c s dng hun luyn trn d liu qua x l, vi cc siu tham s chnh nh:

  • Learning rate: 0.001, gip tc hi t n nh m khng gy dao ng ln.
  • Batch size: 64, cn bng gia tc tnh ton v mc hc ca m hnh.
  • Dropout: 0.2, gim thiu hin tng overfitting.
  • Epochs: 80, m bo m hnh hc y cc mi lin h phc tp trong d liu.

6.2 Phng php nh gi

M hnh LSTM c nh gi bng:

  • Hm Loss: L ch s nh gi mc sai lch gia d on ca m hnh v gi tr thc t. Trong trng hp ny, m hnh LSTM s dng hm categorical cross-entropy tnh ton loss, gip o lng chnh xc ca d on phn loi a lp.

  • Perplexity: L ch s o lng kh nng d on ca m hnh ngn ng, phn nh mc "kh khn" m m hnh gp phi khi d on t hoc k t tip theo. Perplexity thp hn cho thy m hnh d on chnh xc hn, trong khi gi tr cao cho thy m hnh ang gp kh khn trong vic hiu ng cnh ca d liu.

  • Perplexity thp (gn 1) ngha l m hnh ang d on tt v t "ngc nhin" trc d liu.

  • Perplexity cao (ln hn 10, c th n 100 hoc cao hn) ch ra rng m hnh khng hiu tt ng cnh hoc d liu u vo, v do d on ca n km chnh xc hn.

  • Perplexity c tnh theo cng thc sau:

$ \text{Perplexity} = e^{\text{Loss}} $

Trong :

  • ( e ) l c s t nhin (khong 2.718).
  • Loss l gi tr hm loss m m hnh t c.

V d:

  • Nu perplexity = 1, m hnh d on hon ho, tc l n khng gp phi kh khn g khi d on t tip theo.
  • Nu perplexity = 10, m hnh c chnh xc trung bnh nhng vn cha ti u hon ton.
  • Nu perplexity = 100, m hnh gp nhiu kh khn trong vic d on chnh xc.

6.3 Kt qu thc nghim

Hiu sut m hnh LSTM

  • Hm mt mt (Loss): Qua qu trnh hun luyn, hm mt mt gim u qua cc epoch v t gi tr cui cng l 0.0274 ti epoch 72. iu ny cho thy m hnh hc tt t d liu hun luyn v hi t n nh, vi s sai lch gia d on v gi tr thc t rt nh. Mc loss thp ny chng t rng m hnh c kh nng d on chnh xc v hiu qu.
  • Perplexity: Gi tr perplexity ca m hnh l 1.0278, ch ra rng m hnh c kh nng d on cc chui vn bn mt cch rt chnh xc. Perplexity thp nh vy gn bng 1, cho thy m hnh khng gp kh khn khi to ra cc d on tip theo trong chui, ng thi phn nh kh nng hiu ng cnh v tnh ton xc sut cho cc phn t tip theo trong chui.

6.4. Phn tch kt qu

6.4.1. u im ca h thng

  • Tch hp lin mch:
    H thng kt hp hiu qu Apache Kafka v Spark Streaming, cho php x l d liu thi gian thc vi tr thp. Tnh nng fault tolerance ca Spark m bo d liu khng b mt ngay c khi c li xy ra.

  • Kh nng t ng ha:
    Pipeline t ng ha ton b quy trnh t thu thp d liu n sinh vn bn, gip tit kim ng k thi gian v cng sc so vi quy trnh th cng. Hn na, vic tch hp vi API Twitter cho php ng bi t ng, tng hiu qu chin dch tip th.

  • Cht lng vn bn:
    Cc bi vit sinh ra c tnh sng to cao v ph hp vi ch Black Friday. iu ny gip nng cao kh nng tip cn khch hng v t c mc tiu tip th.

6.4.2. Hn ch

  • Kch thc d liu:
    Tp d liu t Twitter API c th cha ln m hnh hc c y cc ng cnh phc tp.

  • Ph thuc vo cu hnh:
    Pipeline ph thuc vo cu hnh Kafka v Spark. Bt k s c no trong cu hnh ca mt trong hai thnh phn ny u c th nh hng n hiu sut tng th.

  • Gii hn ca m hnh:
    M hnh LSTM hin ti ch x l tt vi chui u vo c nh (100 k t). iu ny c th lm gim kh nng hc cc ng cnh di hn hoc phc tp hn.

  • Tim nng ca h thng:

Bng cch tch hp cc cng c tin tin nh Apache NiFi, Apache Kafka, Spark, v cc m hnh hc su, h thng khng ch tit kim thi gian m cn tng cng kh nng tip cn khch hng mt cch linh hot v hiu qu.
    Kt qu thc nghim cho thy m hnh c kh nng to ra cc bi ng vi ni dung ph hp, h tr ti u ha chin lc tip th v ngun lc.

  • Thch thc v hn ch:
    Tuy nhin, d n cng gp phi mt s thch thc quan trng, bao gm:

    • Nng cao cht lng ni dung to ra.
    • m bo tnh chnh xc v sng to ca cc bi ng.
    • Gim thiu li ng ngha v ci thin kh nng din t t nhin.

    Mt hng nghin cu tim nng l tch hp cc m hnh ngn ng tin tin nh GPT-4 hoc cc kin trc Transformer hin i, gip tng cng hiu sut v cht lng u ra.

  • Kh nng m rng ng dng:
    H thng c th c m rng ng dng sang cc lnh vc khc nh:

    • Dch v khch hng t ng.
    • H thng h tr ni dung.
    • C nhn ha tri nghim ngi dng.

    Vic kt hp thm cc ngun d liu phong ph v ci thin kh nng x l theo thi gian thc s tip tc thc y tim nng ng dng ca gii php Text Generation trong cc bi cnh cng ngh hin i.

  • Trin vng tng lai:
    Vi nhng ci tin ny, h thng ha hn s tr thnh mt cng c h tr c lc cho nhiu doanh nghip trong bi cnh nhu cu v ni dung sng to v t ng ha ngy cng tng cao.

8. Ph lc (Appendices)

  • Do nhng thay i trong chnh sch ca Twitter, vic s dng API trc tip t ti khon c nhn thu thp d liu tr nn kh khn hn. C th, ngi dng phi tr thm chi ph nu mun tip tc khai thc d liu thng qua API ca Twitter.

  • khc phc vn ny, nhm quyt nh chuyn sang s dng RapidAPI, mt nn tng cung cp API t nhiu dch v mng x hi khc nhau, trong bao gm c Twitter. RapidAPI mang li li th l d dng truy cp vo nhiu API khc nhau thng qua mt giao din chung, ng thi gip gim bt cc ro cn k thut lin quan n vic cu hnh v tch hp API ring l.

  • Song song , t ng ha qu trnh thu thp v x l d liu, nhm s dng Apache NiFi mt cng c mnh m trong vic xy dng lung x l d liu (workflow). Apache NiFi cung cp nhiu processor chuyn dng, gip h tr vic kt ni vi cc API trn RapidAPI, thu thp d liu theo thi gian thc, v y d liu ny vo cc h thng lu tr hoc phn tch. Vi giao din ko-th trc quan v kh nng m rng linh hot, NiFi gip n gin ha qu trnh tch hp, gim thiu sai st v tit kim thi gian trin khai.

y l workflow c thit lp trong NiFi.

  • Ti generate FlowFile thit lp filter chn lc d liu

  • Sau khi d liu c thu nhp s c truyn ln Kafka thng qua processor PublishKafka ti y s to Producer

  • V nhn d liu ti t Producer ta s tin hnh khi to Consumer thng qua lnh kafka-console-consumer.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic blackfriday2 --from-beginning --max-messages 100
  • Lu : cc topic phi trng khp vi nhau v topic phi c to trc trong Kafka. Ta thu c d liu nhn c t Consumer

T y ta s tin hnh tin x l d liu em d liu thc hin vic trainning model.
